high_descs: Walk ahead to the edge of the counter and turn left.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn around and veer left to the fridge.
Place the apple in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment and then take the apple out.
Turn right and walk all the way to the end of the counter.
Place the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in a microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the apple from the counter that's behind the spoon.
Walk around the island and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the apple in the fridge on the top shelf, close the door, open the door, take the apple out, close the door.
Turn and walk to the microwave on the left side at the end of the counter.
Open the microwave door, place the apple in the microwave, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To chill an apple and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the apple from the back of the counter.
Turn to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the freezer door, place the apple inside, close the freezer door. Open the freezer door, remove the apple, close the freezer door.
Turn around to the right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple inside, close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a frozen apple into a microwave.
